verbose_text: It has been demonstrated that several target mRNAs are directly regulated by miR-206, including Cdc42, estrogen receptor alpha (ERalpha), Notch3, liver X receptor alpha (LXRalpha), high mobility group box 3 like pseudogene (Hmgb3) and c-Met, among which Notch3 was hypothesized to be a direct target gene of miR-206 in this study.
evidence: directly regulated by miR-206, including Cdc42, estrogen receptor alpha (ERalpha), Notch3, liver X receptor alpha
